#: ../../certificates.rst:5
msgid "TLS certificates"
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:7
msgid ""
"An SSL/TLS certificate is a digital object issued by a Certificate "
"Authority (CA). The certificate is used to verify the identity of an host"
" and to establish encrypted communication channels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:10
msgid ""
"Upon install, NethServer 8 uses a default self-signed certificate for all"
" TLS services, including the Web user interface. NethServer 8 can request"
" valid `Let's Encrypt <https://letsencrypt.org/>`_ certificates using "
"`traefik <https://traefik.io/>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:13
msgid ""
"Requesting Let's Encrypt is possible if the following requirements are "
"met:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:15
msgid ""
"the server must be reachable from outside on port 80. Make sure your port"
" 80 is open to the public Internet (you can check with sites like `CSM "
"<http://www.canyouseeme.org/>`_)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:17
msgid ""
"the domains that you want the certificate for must be public domain names"
" associated to server own public IP. Make sure you have public DNS name "
"pointing to your server (you can check with sites like `VDNS "
"<http://viewdns.info/>`_)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:21
msgid "Wild card certificates (i.e. ``*.nethserver.org``) are not supported."
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:23
msgid ""
"If above requirements are met, you can obtain a valid certificate for a "
"domain by following these steps:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:25
msgid "access the ``Settings`` page and click the ``TLS certificates`` card"
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:26 ../../certificates.rst:28
msgid "click on :guilabel:`Request certificate` button"
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:27
msgid "enter the node FQDN and select the node"
msgstr ""

#: ../../certificates.rst:30
msgid ""
"The procedure will take a while, but the system will notify you when the "
"certificate is ready. The Let's Encrypt certificate is automatically "
"renewed 30 days before expiration date."
msgstr ""

